Package SampleCombiDevice

package SampleCombiDevice
  • Klassen
    Klasse
    Beschreibung
    CashDrawer
    Class implementing the CashDrawerInterface for the sample combi device.
    CashDrawerFactory
    Factory class for combined device sample drawer implementation
    Device
    Base of a JposDevice based implementation of JavaPOS CashDrawer, Keylock, LineDisplay,MSR, POSKeyboard, Scanner and ToneIndicator device service implementations for the sample device implemented in CombiSim.tcl.
    For a complete list of possible commands and responses, look at the comments at the beginning of the device simulator script.
    Device.DisplayCoordinates
    Helper class for AdditionalData property of DisplayText class used for synchronous or asynchronous processing.
    Device.TrackData
    Helper class that stores MSR track data.
